Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 绚都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边我来对付 你们去把牢房的锁打开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么屋顶会打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 大概他也在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个半吊子混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万丈 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是更多的是悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是搜查官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要重蹈覆辙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我最后的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要救出雏实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后被有马先生杀死
Comment: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:36.14,OP,,0,0,0,,/----OP----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:42.22,OP,,0,0,0,,例えば目が覚めて「すべては幻だ」って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:48.39,OP,,0,0,0,,奇跡めいた妄想を叶えて欲しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.12,OP,,0,0,0,,僕が描いた罪で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.76,OP,,0,0,0,,結末を満たさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:15.64,OP,,0,0,0,,壊し続けた僕は何かを救えた？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:21.70,OP,,0,0,0,,変わり果てた今に革命のナイフ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}ほどけるように刺して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:29.77,OP,,0,0,0,,光に満ちたさよならを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:33.37,OP,,0,0,0,,I will miss you, I will miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}罰を僕に与えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:43.43,OP,,0,0,0,,君はまだ僕を愛してはくれるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:49.66,OP,,0,0,0,,「僕じゃなきゃ」「僕じゃダメだ」「僕じゃなきゃ」がループする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:56.01,OP,,0,0,0,,僕を刺したナイフさえも  いつかきっと光を射すから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:42.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,希望某天醒来 发现一切都是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:48.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我多想这种奇迹般的妄想能成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,不要让我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,成为故事的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:15.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,破坏众多存在的我 又拯救了什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:21.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,给面目全非的如今 一场革命的刀光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}仿佛要彻底获得解脱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:29.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,渴求那个充满光明的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}给我应有的惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:43.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,你仍旧愿意爱我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:49.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,陷入「非我不可」「我不行的」「非我不可」的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:56.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,刺向我的刀光 迟早也会毁灭那片光明
Comment: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,/----02-----
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有马贵将...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:33.41,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\pos(578.667,965)}白\N色\N{\xshad4\bord1\c&H101010&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}黑\N暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子叫董香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得像我 很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,董香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚都 还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次 再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能保护好她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪我...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要想着靠自责来减轻自己的罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死的是你该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...这家伙在吃喰种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾岛他为了保护董香和绚都才对姐姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我想借着责怪雾岛让自己心里更好受一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我又让他们失去了父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想保护他人真的很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:07:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便自己想去保护 但往往还是会失去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这种想法确实是很珍贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要保护重要之人的这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么 为什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先退下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但以我的立场 也只能和你战斗了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也一样想救雏实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我了 去保护雏实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋老姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这就累趴下了啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,董香 绚都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 好难过 好难过 好难过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说我为什么难过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想到这是最后一次看到佐佐木准特等百感交集的神情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎的就有点难过呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大拇指突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚都 董香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要夺走我的一切吗 有马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走姐姐 还有我的希望...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个不断失去的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一的愿望就是能够延续
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望自己的行动和所生活的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定会保护好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四方先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太难了啊 董香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说一会儿见...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:11:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绚都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋雏实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有丝毫的迟疑和犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有马先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我不想和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你陪我训练过很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这还是第一次认真较量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管只有那么一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防守有些偏颇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面左边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的右眼这侧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一瞬的延迟 将影响到下一招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血的味道好重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急停止措施已经启动了 要穿过这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗 不跟他一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果留下来 他一定会顾着保护我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信研吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又把它启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再死一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,645次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我能够给予你致命伤的次数
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是我放过你的次数
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你选择了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把有马先生拖在这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你身上花的时间都是白费的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点认真打的意思了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送昆克来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:14:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是用枭的赫包制成的昆克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是它的第一个对手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧 金木研
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力啊 青年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮你一把好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算为了小雏实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真血腥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今天真是太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位感觉如何...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馅饼很好吃 给我再来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么爱支那家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从下面?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,董香她们逃出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够什么够啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你就觉得自己争取到充足的时间了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完成任务了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就凭我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你在 我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是兔子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是没找到活下去的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会找到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得捡回一条命 可别白白浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那话怎么说的「为了他人帅气地去死」来着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:18:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候只想和你一起活下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直说 直到你听进去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再难看 也要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反复推翻自己做出的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次次重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无趣至极 丑态毕露 俗不可耐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优柔寡断 软弱之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真实的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特等级别的「V」居然全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好好谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好像是搞错入口了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我谢罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆脱过去的二福冲刺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好景致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不想再争斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来和平解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚没法轻易战胜他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是让你屈服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 幸好我做了嘉纳的手术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫子是利世的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和金木同款的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是利世小姐的赫子 真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧多二福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对「V」以及和修都不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底希望什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超和平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请你自己咽气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了 以你现在的状态...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在杀死对方之前 战斗是不会结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很符合你的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续这种战斗是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至不打算杀我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,败北吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当了18年搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是第一次遇到让我束手无策的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我再问你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不打算给我致命一击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
